videos.description: Bryce Love breaks a tackle and runs for an impressive 61-yard touchdown to score early for Stanford.
videos.headline: Love TD gets Stanford on the board

videos.description: Manny Wilkins is sacked by Arizona State's Mike Tyler for a loss of 21 yards taking Stanford out of field goal range and forcing a punt.
videos.headline: Arizona State's sack halts Stanford's drive

videos.description: Kyle Williams  breaks tackles for a 49-yard run  that helps Arizona State get on the board with a field goal.
videos.headline: Williams' run leads to Arizona State field goal

videos.description: Bryce Love breaks several tackles on his way to a 43-yard touchdown run to extend Stanford's lead.
videos.headline: Love breaks tackles for rushing TD

videos.description: Demario Richard finds a gap and runs three yards into the end zone to get Arizona State on the board with a touchdown.
videos.headline: Richard gets first Arizona State TD

videos.description: K.J. Costello connects with JJ Arcega-Whiteside for a 12-yard touchdown for Stanford's second scoring drive of the second quarter.
videos.headline: Arcega-Whiteside leaps over defender for TD

videos.description: N'Keal Harry finds an open Ceejhay French-Love for a 14 -yard touchdown to close the gap in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Arizona State chips away at Stanford's lead with TD

videos.description: Bryce Love bursts down the field for a touchdown, part of a 301 rushing yard day.
videos.headline: Love streaks for 59-yard TD

videos.description: Justin Reid intercepts Manny Wilkins' pass to give Stanford the ball on its own 48-yard line.
videos.headline: Reid gets his second interception of the game

videos.description: Damario Richard scores a 2-yard rushing  touchdown to bring Arizona State just one scoring drive away from Stanford.
videos.headline: Arizona State cuts deficit in fourth quarter with TD

videos.description: Bryce Love breaks several tackles for a  31 yard run  which leads to a Stanford field goal.
videos.headline: Love's run leads to Stanford field goal

videos.description: Bryce Love runs for 39-yards, one of his many long runs of the day.
videos.headline: Love breaks off another huge run

videos.description: Stanford's Bryce Love runs all over the Arizona State defense, setting a school rushing record with 301 yards with three touchdowns.
